  <brief_title>Self-Determination Theory and Motivational Interviewing</brief_title>
  <official_title>Developing and Testing of Integrating Self-Determination Theory and Motivational Interviewing Based Diabetic Self-management Program Among Schizophrenic Patients With Diabetes</official_title>
  <sponsors>
