  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Self-Determination Theory and motivational interviewing would be integrated to enhance the&#xD;
      efficacy of diabetic self-management for patients with schizophrenia and Type 2 Diabetes.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Participants would be randomly allocated into either the intervention group or the usual care&#xD;
      group from baseline to 3 months follow-up. The intervention is based on integrated&#xD;
      self-determination theory and motivational interviewing.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
